    "body": "## Problem:\r\n- Lots of redundant text in options docs for \"not allowed in a modeline\", even though we already have a flag that indicates that.\r\n- `deny_in_modelines` is an old vestigial flag only used by `encoding` (which never changes).\r\n\r\n## Solution:\r\n- Generate docs based on the `secure` flag.\r\n- Remove the `deny_in_modelines` flag (`kOptFlagNoML`).\r\n\r\n## Future\r\n\r\n- do this for `sandbox-option`, other \"option attributes\" ?",
    "closed_at": null,
